      <title>特斯拉將全自動駕駛軟體的價格下調三分之一至 8,000 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-cuts-price-full-self-driving-software-by-third-8000-2024-04-21/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[週六，特斯拉將其全自動駕駛(FSD) 駕駛員輔助軟體在美國的價格從12,000 美元下調至8,000 美元，執行長 Elon Musk 重申了他對自動駕駛技術的承諾。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-cuts-price-full-self-driving-software-by-third-8000-2024-04-21/</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 04:04:02 GMT</pubDate>
